<i>noun</i>: 훈련병 [훌ː련병], 영입 [영입], 공모 [공모] <i>verb</i>: 충원하다 [충원하다], 채용하다 [채ː용하다], 영입하다 [영이파다], 모집하다 [모지파다], 공모하다 [공모하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>훈련병 [훌ː련병]</dt><br>
<dd>recruit</dd><br>
<dd>각 부대에 배치되기 전에 훈련 기관에서 훈련을 받는 병사.</dd><br>
<dd>A soldier who is being trained at a training institution before being assigned to a unit.</dd><br>
<dt>영입 [영입]</dt><br>
<dd>engaging; scout; recruit</dd><br>
<dd>회사나 정당 등에 함께 일할 사람을 받아들임.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of accepting someone to work for a company, political party, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>공모 [공모]</dt><br>
<dd>recruit</dd><br>
<dd>일반에게 널리 공개하여 모집함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of opening positions, such as for a job or enterprise, etc., to the public and recruiting.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>충원하다 [충원하다]</dt><br>
<dd>supplement the personnel; recruit</dd><br>
<dd>모자라거나 필요한 인원수를 채우다.</dd><br>
<dd>To add more personnel when there is a shortage or need.</dd><br>
<dt>채용하다 [채ː용하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. recruit; hire</dd><br>
<dd>사람을 뽑아서 쓰다.</dd><br>
<dd>To hire an employee.</dd><br>
<dd>2. adopt; apply</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 의견이나 방안 등을 고르거나 받아들여서 쓰다.</dd><br>
<dd>To select or accept an opinion, way, etc., and apply it.</dd><br>
<dt>영입하다 [영이파다]</dt><br>
<dd>engage; scout; recruit</dd><br>
<dd>회사나 정당 등에 함께 일할 사람을 받아들이다.</dd><br>
<dd>To accept someone to work for a company, political party, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>모집하다 [모지파다]</dt><br>
<dd>recruit; collect</dd><br>
<dd>사람이나 작품, 물건 등을 일정한 조건에 맞게 널리 알려 뽑거나 모으다.</dd><br>
<dd>To select or collect people, pieces of work, goods, etc., according to certain criteria by announcing the process publicly.</dd><br>
<dt>공모하다 [공모하다]</dt><br>
<dd>recruit</dd><br>
<dd>일반에게 널리 공개하여 모집하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To open positions, such as for a job or enterprise, etc., to the public, and in this way recruit.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>